************************************************************************************************************************
                                        Welcome to the Path Planning Algorithm

Providing Detect and Avoid Capabilities with route recapture using Reinforcement Learning via
the Monte Carlo Tree Search.
************************************************************************************************************************

************************************************************************************************************************
                                                   Running the Notebook
************************************************************************************************************************

To run the PPA Jupyter notebook:

1. Install Jupyter: https://jupyter.org/
2. From your terminal run: jupyter notebook
3. Go to the PPA/Jupyter Notebooks/ directory and open Path-Planning-Algorithm.ipynb

